%% InsureChat v3.0 — RAG Chat Request Sequence Diagram
%% Full 7-step pipeline: User → Streamlit → FastAPI → Tools → LLM → Response

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant ST as 🖥️ Streamlit<br/>(8501/8502)
    participant API as ⚙️ FastAPI<br/>(8000)
    participant RL as 🛡️ Rate Limiter
    participant IV as 🔒 Input Validator
    participant PII1 as 🕵️ Presidio<br/>(Input PII)
    participant EMB as 📐 Embedder
    participant GEM_E as ☁️ Gemini<br/>Embedding API
    participant VDB as 🗄️ ChromaDB
    participant LLM as 🤖 LLM Router
    participant CLAUDE as ☁️ Claude<br/>Sonnet
    participant GEM_F as ☁️ Gemini<br/>Flash (Fallback)
    participant OV as ✅ Output Validator
    participant PII2 as 🕵️ Presidio<br/>(Output PII)
    participant IC as 🏷️ Intent Classifier
    participant HAIKU as ☁️ Claude<br/>Haiku
    participant AL as 📊 Analytics Logger
    participant DB as 💾 SQLite
    participant LOG as 📝 JSONL Audit

    U->>ST: Type question
    ST->>API: POST /chat/{type}<br/>{ query, session_id }
    API->>RL: Check rate limit (10/min)
    
    alt Rate limit exceeded
        RL-->>API: 429 Too Many Requests
        API-->>ST: Rate limit error
        ST-->>U: "Please wait..."
    end
    
    RL->>IV: validate_input(query)
    
    Note over IV: Step 1: Length Check
    IV->>IV: check_length(query, 500)
    
    alt Input too long
        IV-->>API: { blocked: true, reason: "input_too_long" }
        API-->>ST: Fallback message
        ST-->>U: "Message too long"
    end
    
    Note over IV: Step 2: Injection Scan
    IV->>IV: check_injection(query)<br/>12 regex patterns
    
    alt Injection detected
        IV-->>API: { blocked: true, reason: "injection_detected" }
        API->>AL: Log blocked interaction
        AL->>DB: INSERT message (blocked)
        AL->>LOG: Append audit entry
        API-->>ST: Fallback message
        ST-->>U: "I can only help with..."
    end
    
    Note over IV,PII1: Step 3: PII Detection & Redaction
    IV->>PII1: analyze(query, entities)
    PII1-->>IV: PII results
    IV->>PII1: anonymize(query, results)
    PII1-->>IV: sanitized_query
    IV-->>API: { valid: true, sanitized_query, pii_detected }
    
    Note over EMB,GEM_E: Step 4: Query Embedding
    API->>EMB: embed_query(sanitized_query)
    EMB->>GEM_E: embed_content(text,<br/>task=RETRIEVAL_QUERY,<br/>dim=768)
    GEM_E-->>EMB: 768-dim vector
    EMB-->>API: embedding[]
    
    Note over VDB: Step 5: Vector Retrieval
    API->>VDB: retrieve_chunks(embedding,<br/>collection, top_k=5)
    VDB->>VDB: query(cosine similarity)
    VDB-->>API: { chunks, sources, scores }
    
    alt Low confidence (< 0.60)
        API->>IC: classify_intent(query)
        IC->>HAIKU: messages.create()
        HAIKU-->>IC: intent category
        API->>AL: Log low-confidence
        API-->>ST: "Not enough info..."
        ST-->>U: Fallback message
    end
    
    Note over LLM,CLAUDE: Step 6: LLM Generation
    API->>LLM: call_claude(query, chunks,<br/>sources, chatbot_type)
    LLM->>LLM: build_rag_prompt()
    Note over LLM: Step 5.5: Load conversation history<br/>(last N turns, token-trimmed)
    LLM->>LLM: Prepend history turns to messages[]
    LLM->>CLAUDE: messages.create(model=sonnet,<br/>system_prompt, history + user_message,<br/>max_tokens=1024, temp=0.2)
    
    alt Claude API Error
        CLAUDE--xLLM: APIError
        LLM->>GEM_F: generate_content(<br/>system + user message)
        GEM_F-->>LLM: fallback response
    end
    
    CLAUDE-->>LLM: response + token count
    LLM-->>API: { response, tokens_used, model }
    
    Note over OV,PII2: Step 7: Output Validation
    API->>OV: validate_output(response,<br/>chunks, confidence)
    OV->>PII2: mask_pii(response)
    PII2-->>OV: masked_response
    OV->>OV: check_hallucination_phrases()
    OV->>OV: compute_word_overlap()<br/>(threshold: 30%)
    
    alt Hallucination detected
        OV-->>API: { valid: false,<br/>fallback_message }
    end
    
    OV-->>API: { valid: true,<br/>final_response }
    
    Note over IC,HAIKU: Step 8: Intent Classification
    API->>IC: classify_intent(query,<br/>chatbot_type)
    IC->>HAIKU: messages.create(model=haiku,<br/>temp=0, max_tokens=50)
    HAIKU-->>IC: category name
    IC-->>API: intent string
    
    Note over AL,LOG: Step 9: Analytics Logging
    API->>AL: log_interaction({...})
    AL->>DB: INSERT INTO messages
    AL->>LOG: Append JSONL line
    AL-->>API: { message_id }

    Note over API: Step 9.5: Save Conversation Turn
    API->>API: session_store.add_turn(<br/>session_id, sanitized_query,<br/>validated_response)
    
    API-->>ST: ChatResponse {<br/>response, sources,<br/>confidence_score,<br/>llm_used, message_id }
    ST-->>U: Display answer<br/>with sources
